{
 "name": "fyp_quant",
 "description": "Research benchmarking framework studying safety-capability trade-offs in quantized small language models (1.7-7.2B): compares fp16 baseline vs on-the-fly NF4 4-bit / INT8 quantized loading across HarmBench (attack success rate), XSTest (over-refusal), and MMLU (accuracy), with pairwise delta analysis, a Streamlit dashboard, SLURM cluster tooling, and an automated FYP report builder. Note: this project has over 100 source files; consider scoping analysis to a subdirectory for faster results.",
